WEBVTT

00:02:56.120 --> 00:03:02.296
Honestly, uncertainty can make
our life more joyous and spicy.

00:03:02.320 --> 00:03:08.296
Research shows that when
we are uncertain about something,

00:03:08.320 --> 00:03:12.496
we get more happiness in that thing.

00:03:12.520 --> 00:03:17.016
For instance, as compared to recorded
TV people prefer live TV.

00:03:17.040 --> 00:03:18.736
Why?

00:03:18.760 --> 00:03:21.536
Because live TV has greater uncertainty.

00:03:21.560 --> 00:03:23.896
Nobody knows who will win or who will lose,

00:03:23.920 --> 00:03:25.856
and that is exactly what makes it fun.

